msgid "Toolbars"
msgstr "Werkbalken"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:16
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Inhoud"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:19
msgid "Main and Extra Toolbars"
msgstr "Hoofd- en extra werkbalken"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:21
msgid "**Kdenlive** has a *Main Toolbar*,"
msgstr "**Kdenlive** heeft een *Hoofdwerkbalk*,"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:29
msgid "an *Extra Toolbar*, which by default contains the **Render** button,"
msgstr "een *Werkbalk Extra*, die standaard de knop **Renderen** bevat,"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:37
msgid "and a status toolbar."
msgstr "en een statuswerkbalk."

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:44
msgid "For more info on the status toolbar see :ref:`editing`."
msgstr "Voor meer informatie over de statusbalk zie :ref:`editing`."

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:48
msgid "Configuring the Toolbars"
msgstr "De werkbalken configureren"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:50
msgid ""
"The tools that are available on these are defined in :menuselection:"
"`Settings --> Configure Toolbars`."
msgstr ""
"De hulpmiddelen die hierop beschikbaar zijn worden gedefinieerd in :"
"menuselection:`Instellingen --> Werkbalken configureren`."

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:59
msgid "Hiding and Showing the Toolbars"
msgstr "De werkbalken verbergen en tonen"

#: ../../user_interface/toolbars.rst:61
msgid ""
"You can toggle the hiding and showing of the toolbars from the  :ref:"
"`view_menu` using the :menuselection:`Main Toolbar` and :menuselection:"
"`Extra Toolbar` menu items. You can also control this from the :ref:"
"`toolbars_shown` menu item in the :menuselection:`Settings` menu."
msgstr ""
"U kunt het verbergen en tonen van de werkbalken omschakelen het de :ref:"
"`view_menu` en gebruik van de menu-items :menuselection:`Hoofswerkbalk` en :"
"menuselection:`Extra werkbalk`. U kunt deze ook besturen vanuit het menu-"
"item :ref:`toolbars_shown` in het menu :menuselection:`Instellingen`."
